{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"000199a4-6875-4848-81e0-02f0eeab357d","content":"Here are the MSBuild evaluation performance issues in this project:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Recursive wildcard glob (`**\\*.*`) — **High Impact**\n**Line 9 of `EvalHeavy.csproj`:**\n```xml\n<AdditionalFiles Include=\"**\\*.*\" Exclude=\"**\\bin\\**;**\\obj\\**\" />\n```\nThis forces MSBuild to walk the **entire directory tree** on every evaluation. It's especially expensive in repos with deep `node_modules`, large `obj`/`bin` leftovers, or many files. Prefer explicit file lists or narrower globs (e.g., `*.txt`).\n\n### 2. File I/O via property function — **Medium Impact**\n**Line 13 of `EvalHeavy.csproj`:**\n```xml\n<BuildNotes>$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))</BuildNotes>\n```\nCalling `System.IO.File.ReadAllText` during evaluation performs **synchronous disk I/O on every evaluation pass** (IDE reloads, restore, build). This blocks the evaluation thread. Move file reads to a target that runs only during build instead.\n\n### 3. Deep import chain — **Low-Medium Impact**\n```\nEvalHeavy.csproj → level1.props → level2.props → level3.props\n```\nThree levels of chained `<Import>` files. Each import is a separate file open + parse + merge. In this project the chain is short, but the pattern doesn't scale — as the chain grows, evaluation time grows linearly and the dependency graph becomes hard to reason about. Flatten where possible.\n\n---\n\n**Summary of recommendations:**\n| Issue | Fix |\n|---|---|\n| `**\\*.*` glob | Narrow the glob or list files explicitly |\n| `ReadAllText` in property | Move to a build-time target (`<Target>`) |\n| Nested imports | Flatten into fewer files |\n\nThe recursive glob is by far the biggest offender — it alone can add hundreds of milliseconds in large directory trees.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3828462c-5c59-4232-9f04-6b7c14138289","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me analyze the MSBuild evaluation performance issues in this project.","outputTokens":530},"id":"0528710d-74ff-4e5d-a02a-1e35a05928b9","timestamp":"2026-04-04T01:05:13.487Z","parentId":"3c369eeb-d045-4096-916a-718a537ab6cd"}
